      </author_list>
      <publication_year>1992</publication_year>
      <description>
       Introduction and overview document for the Multi-look Color series of products from the
       VO1/VO2-M-VIS-5-DIM-V1.0 PDS3 data set, the source data set for all of the multispectral DIM
       (Digital Image Model) products in this bundle.  Please note that this document is partially deprecated!
       This bundle does not follow the directory structure and naming conventions of those archive volumes,
       and its member products are formatted differently. However, this document still provides invaluable
       information on the provenance and characteristics of these data. It was stored as 'document/volinfo.txt'
       in volumes 8-14 (vo_2008 - vo_2014) of that data set. We have discarded its SFDU label and stripped
       form-feed characters; it is otherwise unchanged.
      </description>
